parameters:
\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>But since I'm alone, I feel so relaxed~ No need to worry
about anything, I might as well play a game on my
smartphone...

\nc<Saki>(I thought all the executive officers went to the year-end
party, why... out of all people, it had to be the one I'm
least comfortable with...)

\nc<Executive Officer>Playing smartphone games in the sacred office, huh? This
could be grounds for forced reassignment.

\nc<Saki>(Don't reassign someone over such a trivial matter!)
P-please, just this once, forgive me...

\nc<Executive Officer>Hmm, I can't help but give in when Saki-kun asks. However,
there have been rumors that your recent performance hasn't
been very impressive...

\nc<Executive Officer>If you go out with me for a bit, you won't have to worry
about that anymore.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>(Damn, it's only my first year and already talking about
performance... But... if I catch the eye of an executive
officer, maybe my corporate life will get easier.)
\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>Ehehe, how did you know what I was about to offer to do...

\nc<Executive Officer>Heh heh, shall we go right now? (I couldn't make a move
because of Meary usually... but I shouldn't have to worry
about that anymore.)

\nc<Executive Officer>Whoa, don't struggle. I'm counting on you from now on, Saki-
chan?

parameters.name: 【凌辱】女子高生セリフ8「だめぇぇぇぇ！」
